config FS_APPS_IPIPED
	select FS_APPS_DBUS
	select FS_APPS_DBUS_DAEMON
	select FS_APPS_GLIB
	select FS_APPS_READLINE
	select FS_APPS_NCURSES
	bool "ipiped"
	default n
	help
	Ipiped is an application capable of receiving
	through dbus messages commands to configure
	and control IPIPE path and its modules.
	
	When used along with other libraries it can provide
	autowhite balance/autoexposure algorithms
